===アーティファクトチャージ===

In a world where the light of justice does not
shine, a hidden auction house is illuminated by a
mysterious light. The nobles with wicked smiles
are revealed. Their insatiable, bloated desires
have surpassed normalcy.

\py[10]And then, the host appears on stage. Next
to them is Sol, wearing a collar.

\py[10]The collar is engraved with a magic spell
that seals her abilities, leaving Sol in a state
where she cannot even resist or oppose turning
back into a dragon.

\n<Kidnapper>Ladies and gentlemen, nobles, merchants, and
esteemed individuals! Tonight, we are pleased to
introduce to you this young lady! In fact, she is
none other than the 'Golden Dragon's child'!

\n<People Snatcher>\py[10]Although she may appear in human form now,
her golden tail is the proof that she is indeed
the Golden Dragon!

\n<People Snatcher>\py[10]This existence, more valuable than an equal
weight of gold! Spend a dazzling night with this
beautiful and rare girl, starting at 1000 gold
coins!

\n<People Snatcher>\py[10]Now, now! How about it? Those who are
interested, raise your hand while holding a bag of
gold coins!

\py[10]The nobles eagerly raise their hands and
announce their prices. The one who offers the
highest price will gain the right to embrace Sol.
It's a despicable sight, even pigs would turn away
from it.

\py[10]The night of desire progresses. What will
become of Sol's fate...
